               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I was coming up the street about four o'clock; a great num<lb></lb>ber of women were outside the door; these boots were on the pavement, and I picked them up and went about 100 yards; he came after me and said, "Give me those boots," and I threw them away.</p>
